race.comment: SHE'S IMPECCABLE (2) looks tough to hold out. Hit the line hard for a close-up fifth second-up and should be at her top now. Extra trip is a plus and drops back a notch. Hard to beat. WHAT A FLIRT (1) is also a last start winner, overcoming a slow start before running on hard to score narrowly. Trip suits and will be hitting the line hard again. FROST YOURSELF (3) has been well off best form in two runs back from a break. Well placed this company and fitter again won't get a better chance to show something. FINE REBEL (5) is fitter for two runs back and worth noting both career wins have been on soft ground. Gets a chance to fire.
